stories_text_raw:
As a Data User, I want to process deletions for a specific date, so that I can ensure data integrity and accuracy.
As a UI Designer, I want to redesign the resources page, so that users have an improved experience.
As a UI Designer, I want to report user testing results, so that stakeholders are informed of the testing outcomes.
As a DevOps Engineer, I want to get New Relic data, so that I can monitor application performance.
As a Broker User, I want to sync D1 file generation, so that data is consistent and up-to-date.
As a Broker Team Member, I want to update SQL codes, so that they are clear and maintainable.
As a Broker Team Member, I want to update derivation logic, so that data is accurately processed.
As a Broker Team Member, I want to derive the funding agency code, so that data quality and completeness are ensured.
As an Agency User, I want to map federal action obligations, so that they are correctly associated with Atom Feed data.
As a FABS User, I want to update FABS submissions, so that data is accurate and current.
As a FABS User, I want to update the FABS sample file, so that it reflects the latest changes.
As a FABS User, I want to deactivate the publish button, so that accidental publications are prevented.
As a FABS User, I want to derive the historical FABS loader, so that historical data is accurately processed.
As a FABS User, I want to update frontend URLs, so that users can access the correct pages.
As a Developer, I want to improve logging, so that issues can be effectively diagnosed and resolved.
As a Developer, I want to index domain models, so that data is efficiently stored and retrieved.
As a Developer, I want to access broker application data, so that I can perform maintenance and updates.
As an Owner, I want to send USAspending grant records, so that they are shared with relevant parties.
As an Owner, I want to create a user testing summary, so that stakeholders are informed of the testing outcomes.
As an Owner, I want to design an audit, so that the system is thoroughly evaluated and improved.
As an Owner, I want to reset the environment, so that it is restored to a default state.
As a DABS User, I want to update header information, so that it is accurate and consistent.
